creative_body:
Haa tengok ni! Serius takkan menyesal sebab kebaya ni untuk korang yang nak tampil anggun, eksklusif & on-the-go! 😍

Dah la cantik, minimal & paling penting TAK PERLU GOSOK! Sarung je terus siap, sesuai sangat untuk hari-hari sibuk atau bila nak cepat!

Warna mana satu idaman hati?? Cepat grab sekarang!

Jangan biarkan luka jadi semakin teruk! 🚨

Klinik kami menawarkan rawatan luka yang komprehensif menggunakan Rejim Khas Dr Luka, bukan sekadar cuci luka biasa (dressing)

Kami merawat pelbagai jenis luka, termasuk:
✅ Luka Kencing Manis (Diabetic Wound)
✅ Luka/ Ulser Vena (Venous Ulcer)
✅ Pembedahan Kecil (Minor Operations)
✅ Penjagaan Luka Selepas Pembedahan (Caesarean, Bypass, dll.)
✅ Luka Kemalangan

💉 Rawatan cepat & selamat, sebelum luka jadi serius.

📲 WhatsApp kami hari ini & book rawatan anda segera!

creative_body:
🦵 Lutut berbunyi & sakit bila berjalan?

Jangan biar sampai susah nak bergerak, itu mungkin tanda Knee Osteoarthritis (OA), masalah sendi yang biasa berlaku bila rawan lutut dah mula haus 😣

Tanda-tandanya termasuk:

✅ Kurangkan sakit & bengkak
✅ Tingkatkan pergerakan sendi
✅ Elak kerosakan lebih teruk

📍 Mesra Klinik Taman Peruda
📞 019-6755690 | 04-4248165

👉 Jangan tunggu sampai lutut makin teruk, datang dapatkan rawatan hari ni juga!

creative_title: DAPATKAN RAWATAN DI MESRA KLINIK PERUDA
creative_body:
🖐️ Kerap rasa kebas atau sakit di tapak tangan & jari?

Jangan pandang ringan, itu mungkin tanda Carpal Tunnel Syndrome (CTS)! 😣

Ramai sangka cuma lenguh biasa, tapi kalau:
❗ Sakit di jari & tapak tangan
❗ Kerap kebas / rasa semut-semut
❗ Susah nak genggam barang
… tu petanda saraf di pergelangan tangan anda dah mula terhimpit!

Kalau dibiarkan, boleh sampai tahap tak boleh guna tangan dengan betul 😔

Di Mesra Klinik Taman Peruda, kami sediakan rawatan CTS yang selamat, cepat & berkesan, bantu hilangkan sakit dan pulihkan fungsi tangan anda semula 💪

📍 Lokasi: Mesra Klinik Taman Peruda
📞 Hubungi kami: 019-6755690 | 04-4248165

👉 Dapatkan rawatan sekarang sebelum makin teruk. Tangan sihat, kerja pun mudah!

“Bangun pagi terus rasa sendi ketat & sakit? Itu tanda awal masalah serius!” 😣

Ramai ingat sakit sendi, urat & saraf akan hilang sendiri. Tapi hakikatnya, kalau dibiarkan:
❌ Sakit makin teruk
❌ Pergerakan terbatas
❌ Risiko hilang fungsi sendi

Kami di Poliklinik Mesra Taman Peruda sedia membantu untuk masalah seperti:
✅ Frozen Shoulder – bahu kaku & sakit
✅ Knee Osteoarthritis – lutut lemah & berdenyut
✅ Trigger Finger – jari tersangkut & susah diluruskan
✅ Carpal Tunnel Syndrome – kebas/semut-semut di tangan
✅ De Quervain Tenosynovitis – sakit pergelangan bila genggam

💉 Kaedah rawatan terkini & selamat
📆 Hubungi sekarang untuk temujanji

📍 Poliklinik Mesra Taman Peruda
📞 019-675 5690 | 04-424 8165

💬 “Kesihatan sendi anda pelaburan untuk masa depan. Jangan tunggu sampai terlambat.”

Ramai nak kurus, tapi risau cara yang tak selamat 🚫

creative_body:
❄️ Bahu terasa ketat & susah nak angkat tangan?

Hati-hati! Itu mungkin tanda Frozen Shoulder atau bahu beku! 😣

Antara tanda-tanda yang biasa:
⚠️ Sukar angkat tangan melebihi paras bahu
⚠️ Bahu terasa kaku terutamanya waktu pagi

Kalau ya, jangan abaikan tanda ni! Ramai tak tahu, itu mungkin tanda Trigger Finger, keadaan di mana tendon jari dah mula tersepit dan boleh menyebabkan jari terkunci kalau dibiarkan lama 😣

Kalau dikesan awal, rawatan sangat mudah dan cepat!

creative_title: Dapatkan Rawatan Di Mesra Klinik Peruda Hari Ini!
creative_body:
🦵 Lutut berbunyi & sakit bila berjalan?

Jangan biar sampai susah nak bergerak, itu mungkin tanda Knee Osteoarthritis (OA), masalah sendi yang biasa berlaku bila rawan lutut dah mula haus 😣

Tanda-tandanya termasuk:
⚠️ Lutut berbunyi semasa bergerak
⚠️ Sakit bila berjalan atau berdiri lama
⚠️ Lutut rasa panas & mula membengkak

Kalau dibiarkan, sakit boleh jadi semakin teruk sampai sukar nak berdiri lama atau solat dengan sempurna 😔

Di Mesra Klinik Taman Peruda, kami tawarkan rawatan untuk bantu:
✅ Kurangkan sakit & bengkak
✅ Tingkatkan pergerakan sendi
✅ Elak kerosakan lebih teruk

📍 Mesra Klinik Taman Peruda
📞 019-6755690 | 04-4248165

👉 Jangan tunggu sampai lutut makin teruk, datang dapatkan rawatan hari ni juga!

Ramai nak kurus, tapi risau cara yang tak selamat 🚫
Di Poliklinik Mesra Taman Peruda, kami tawarkan program kurus yang:
🩺 Dipantau oleh doktor
📉 Berat badan dipantau konsisten
💬 Ada konsultasi & follow-up setiap minggu

👉 Bukan sahaja turun berat, tapi lebih sihat & yakin dengan diri sendiri ✨

Jangan tunggu lama, mula langkah pertama hari ini ✨”

⚠️ Slot terhad!
📞 Hubungi kami di 016-6755690 / 04-4248165

creative_title: Dapatkan Rawatan Di Mesra Klinik Peruda Hari Ini!
creative_body:
🖐️ Kerap rasa kebas atau sakit di tapak tangan & jari?

Jangan pandang ringan, itu mungkin tanda Carpal Tunnel Syndrome (CTS)! 😣

Ramai sangka cuma lenguh biasa, tapi kalau:
❗ Sakit di jari & tapak tangan
❗ Kerap kebas / rasa semut-semut
❗ Susah nak genggam barang
… tu petanda saraf di pergelangan tangan anda dah mula terhimpit!

Kalau dibiarkan, boleh sampai tahap tak boleh guna tangan dengan betul 😔

Di Mesra Klinik Taman Peruda, kami sediakan rawatan CTS yang selamat, cepat & berkesan, bantu hilangkan sakit dan pulihkan fungsi tangan anda semula 💪

📍 Lokasi: Mesra Klinik Taman Peruda
📞 Hubungi kami: 019-6755690 | 04-4248165

👉 Dapatkan rawatan sekarang sebelum makin teruk. Tangan sihat, kerja pun mudah!

🌞 Goodbye NEM? Say Hello to Solar ATAP!
Just because NEM is over, it doesn’t mean your solar journey has to stop.

Malaysia now has a new solar scheme called ATAP (Accelerated Transition of Energy Program) – and it brings even better benefits for homeowners and businesses.

Here’s why Solar ATAP is a game changer:

✅ You can install solar systems to cover up to 100% of your electricity usage
✅ You earn energy credits based on real electricity market prices – potentially higher returns, especially during peak hours
✅ No more short contract periods – ATAP gives you long-term savings and peace of mind
✅ It is open to all TNB customers – including homes, offices, factories, and shops
✅ Perfect for anyone looking to cut monthly bills and become more energy independent

creative_body:
Nak cari venue yang bukan sekadar luas, tapi boleh angkat prestij event anda ke tahap seterusnya?
Stadium N9 Arena ada semua yang anda perlukan. 🏟️

✨ Kapasiti ribuan tetamu • sesuai untuk konvokesyen, konsert, expo, karnival & acara sukan.
✨ Ruang indoor & outdoor fleksibel • boleh diubah ikut konsep acara.
✨ Sistem audio-visual moden • pastikan setiap acara nampak eksklusif & profesional.
✨ Lokasi strategik di Seremban • mudah diakses, parking luas & selesa untuk pengunjung.

Tak kisah anda penganjur korporat, institusi pendidikan, komuniti atau usahawan, stadium ini direka untuk menjadikan acara anda lebih lancar & berimpak.

📍Lokasi: N9 Arena, Persiaran Perbandaran, 71800 Nilai, Negeri Sembilan.

📞 Untuk maklumat lanjut & tempahan, hubungi YNS Event Management atau terus ke laman web rasmi:
👉 https://n9arena.ubertickets.asia/

creative_body:
🖐 Sakit Jari Tak Boleh Lurus? Hati-Hati, Mungkin Anda Alami "Trigger Finger"!

Jari terasa "klik" bila digerakkan? Sukar meluruskan jari terutama waktu pagi? Itu tanda-tanda Trigger Finger, masalah biasa tapi menyakitkan jika dibiarkan.

Ramai pesakit tak sedar ia boleh dirawat dengan mudah – tak perlu tunggu sampai tahap serius atau perlukan pembedahan. Kami di Poliklinik Mesra Taman Peruda sedia membantu anda dengan rawatan yang berkesan dan selamat.

creative_body:

creative_body:
Sumbangan anda telah memberikan sinar harapan kepada Orang Bebas Berlesen (OBB) yang bercita-cita untuk berjaya. Mereka, seperti individu lain, berhak untuk mencapai kejayaan.

Kesilapan yang pernah mereka lakukan bukan penghalang, malah boleh dijadikan sebagai pengajaran berharga untuk membina masa depan yang lebih baik.

Sumbangan anda bukan sekadar bantuan material, tetapi lebih daripada itu, ia menyalakan kembali semangat dan keyakinan mereka untuk meraih kehidupan yang lebih bermakna.

Ia membuktikan bahawa dengan sedikit bantuan dan sokongan daripada anda, seseorang yang pernah tersasar dapat bangkit kembali dan mencapai kejayaan.

Sumbangan boleh dibuat disini:
https://yayasanamanah.my/infaq/
#YayasanAmanah #Agrication #Parol #CSI #PBSL #Pertanian

Plastic’s in the orange, glass in the brown… but what about our old phones?! Comment below if you know! #iykyk #ytjt
#mobileewaste #KITARMCMC #KITARuntukKITA

E-waste doesn’t just disappear; it circles back in ways we can’t ignore - like toxic contaminants that pollute the environment and come back through your food!
Let’s break the cycle!♻️

Collect your stored old devices at home and recycle through KITAR!
#mobileewaste #KITARMCMC #KITARuntukKITA

Though Tong KITAR may lack the enchantment of true magical beasts, the Drop Points—over 140 in number—are no less elusive to find than a Niffler’s stash! 🗺️✨

With a simple flick of your wand (or rather, a tap on your screen), you can reveal the nearest Drop Point. Begin your quest at kitar.mcmc.gov.my, and discover a Drop Point nearby—no spellcasting required!

creative_title: Build Your Future with IMPERiA College
creative_body:
Start your path to success in Construction & Property Education at IMPERIA, Malaysia!

Here's why we're the top choice for international students:

𝗚𝗹𝗼𝗯𝗮𝗹𝗹𝘆 𝗥𝗲𝗰𝗼𝗴𝗻𝗶𝘇𝗲𝗱: Benefit from MQA accreditation and the exclusive BOVAEP accreditation for the Real Estate Investment and Finance program (a major advantage for your career!).

𝗣𝗶𝗼𝗻𝗲𝗲𝗿𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗘𝗱𝘂𝗰𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻: We are the leader in property education, offering a dynamic and future-proof learning experience.

𝗜𝗻𝘁𝗲𝗿𝗻𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻𝗮𝗹 𝗦𝘁𝘂𝗱𝗲𝗻𝘁 𝘀𝘂𝗽𝗽𝗼𝗿𝘁: Our dedicated international student support team assists you with enrollment, visa applications, airport pick-up, health insurance, and more.

𝗜𝗻𝗱𝘂𝘀𝘁𝗿𝘆 𝗘𝘅𝗽𝗲𝗿𝘁𝗶𝘀𝗲: Benefit from SENTORIA's vast experience and network in the property sector.

𝗪𝗼𝗿𝗸-𝗕𝗮𝘀𝗲𝗱 𝗟𝗲𝗮𝗿𝗻𝗶𝗻𝗴: Gain practical experience through our partnership with Bukit Gambang Resort City.

Join our vibrant international student community in Malaysia and gain the skills to excel in the booming property sector. 

Limited seats available! 

Contact us via WhatsApp today to learn more!

campaign_name: Tadika Langkah Pertama | BA | M3 | Client | Rashdan
creative_body:
🌱 种植秋葵比赛🌱

**问：种植比赛是什么样的活动呢？
*答：*这是一场有趣且具有教育意义的比赛，孩子们会亲自动手种植属于他们自己的蔬菜，这对培养孩子们对园艺的热爱和对健康饮食的了解是个非常好的方法！🌿

**问：谁可以参加此比赛呢？
*答：*比赛向公众开放，年龄从3岁至 9 岁的儿童。👧👦

*问：我们如何开始种植秋葵？*
*答：* First Step Kindergarten 将提供所有必要的材料，包括秋葵种子和土壤。也会发送种植过程的方法，您只需要在特定的时间过来领取即可。

*问：如何分享我们在比赛中的进展？*
*答：*我们鼓励参与者在我们的 Facebook 页面上分享他们种植秋葵的照片和更新。这是激励他人并展示您的园艺技能的绝佳方式！📸🌱

*问：比赛有奖品吗？*
*答：*有！
*如有任何疑问。请致电我们了解更多详情！🏆🎉
期待你的参与！

campaign_name: Tadika Langkah Pertama | BA | M3 | Client | Rashdan
creative_body:
🌱 Grow Your Own Lady's Fingers! 🌱

*Q: What is the "Grow Your Own Food" contest all about?*  
*A:* It's a fun and educational contest where children aged 3 to 9 years old can learn to grow their own lady's fingers (okra). It's a wonderful way to introduce kids to gardening and healthy eating! 🌿

*Q: Who can participate in this contest?*  
*A:* The contest is open to the public, specifically for children between the ages of 3 to 9 years old. 👧👦

*Q: How do we get started with growing lady's fingers?*  
*A:* First Step Kindergarten will provide all the necessary materials, including lady's finger seeds and soil. 

*Q: How can we share our progress in the contest?*  
*A:* We encourage participants to share photos and updates of their growing lady's fingers on our Facebook page. It's a fantastic way to inspire others and showcase your gardening skills! 📸🌱

*Q: Is there a prize for the contest?*  
*A:* Yes! We will have exciting prizes for the best-grown lady's fingers. Call us for more details! 🏆🎉

Setiap perkara yang anda cari dalam talian seperti muat turun gambar atau video akan meninggalkan jejak yang lebih besar daripada yang anda fikirkan! 

Jejak digital tersebut tersimpan dalam memori peranti anda dan lama-kelamaan menyebabkan peranti anda tidak dapat berfungsi dengan baik (lagging). Akhirnya, peranti ini akan dibuang sebagai e-waste. 🌍
 ️
Kurangkan jejak digital anda, kurangkan e-waste.

Jejak digital adalah jejak data yang anda tinggalkan setiap kali anda melayari internet dan membeli-belah atau menghantar mesej dalam talian.  🔍

Data ini boleh digunakan oleh pihak lain untuk pelbagai kegunaan termasuklah pengiklanan barangan dan perkhidmatan, dengan kebenaran pengguna.

Selain itu, jejak digital ini juga memberi kesan kepada alam sekitar? ♻ Anda tahu macam mana? Cuba komen di bawah😉

campaign_name: Lakefront M3 | Awareness | CLIENT | Bryan | PR
creative_title: Talk to our relationship associates today!
creative_body:
Finding the perfect property takes time, but picking the right developer is key! Selecting the right real estate developer is important to ensure your needs are met in the long term.

Here are 4 things you should look out for:
1) The developer's background: Look for a developer with a proven track record, many past projects to review, and deep market knowledge. 
2) Quality of properties offered: Choose a developer known for using top materials and innovative building practices. ️
3) Problem solving skills: A good developer anticipates issues and guides you through a smooth buying journey.
4) Financial knowledge & expertise: Find a developer with strong financial partners, offering competitive options of properties.

At Avaland, we've been crafting communities and enhancing lives for generations. We use top-notch materials, solve problems proactively, and offer expert financial guidance – all to make your home buying journey smooth and successful.

Schedule an appointment to discuss more!

campaign_name: Lakefront M3 | Awareness | CLIENT | Bryan | PR
creative_body:
Buying your first home can be exciting, but also overwhelming! Here's a simple 5-step checklist to guide you on your journey:

1. Identify your reason: Investment or personal haven?
2. Check your credit score: A good score unlocks better loan options!
3. Plan your budget: Factor in loan amount, fees, and future maintenance costs.
4. Explore first-time buyer benefits: Government programs & tax breaks can help!
5. Find the perfect fit: Location, size, and features that match your needs and budget.
We offer a supportive environment, modern amenities, and a reputable developer – all at an attractive price point, from only RM1,800/month. 

Get prepared to own your very first home! Register your interest today.

campaign_name: Lakefront M3 | Awareness | CLIENT | Bryan | PR
creative_body:
Living lakeside shouldn't mean living with leaky faucets and dusty vents! ‍♀️ Sanderling Lakefront Residence cares about your tranquility as much as your stunning view.  That's why we're sharing pro tips to keep your condo happy and healthy:

Filter Frenzy: Bye-bye dust bunnies! Clean or replace your appliance filters for peak performance and fresher air.
Drain the Drama: Don't let sediment stress your water heater! A yearly drain and flush keeps it running smoothly (and saves you $$).
Cleaning Cavalry: Conquer the clutter! Regular cleaning keeps your sanctuary sparkling and your mind at ease.

Want own your dream home? Talk to us today!
